query:
/*+ NoHashJoin(a1 q1 t1 tq1 u1) */ select acc.location,
count(*)
from question AS q1
inner join tag_question AS tq1
on q1.id = tq1.question_id AND q1.view_count >= 10 AND q1.view_count <= 1000
inner join tag AS t1
on t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND t1.name IN ('analytic-number-theory',
'commerce',
'examples-counterexamples',
'ideals',
'indefinite-integrals',
'inequality',
'laplace-transform',
'stochastic-processes',
'systems-of-equations',
'theming',
'uniform-convergence')
inner join answer AS a1
on q1.id = a1.question_id
inner join so_user AS u1
on a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND u1.downvotes >= 10 AND u1.downvotes <= 100000
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = a1.site_id AND s.site_id = t1.site_id AND s.site_id = tq1.site_id AND s.site_id = u1.site_id AND s.site_id = q1.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('drupal',
'math',
'mathoverflow',
'ru',
'salesforce')
inner join badge AS b
on s.site_id = b.site_id AND b.user_id = u1.id AND b.name IN ('Investor',
'Peer Pressure',
'Reviewer',
'Tenacious',
'Vox Populi')
inner join account AS acc
on acc.id = u1.account_id group by acc.location order by count(*) desc LIMIT 100;
